#### Q73. What is wrong with this code?

```cs
void MyFunction()
{
    {
        int a = 10;
        int b = 20;
        int c = a + b;
    }

    Console.WriteLine(c);
}
```

- %OPTION% Variable c is never used; displaying it on the console does not count as usage.
- %OPTION% Variables a and b are never used.
- %OPTION% You cannot place code inside brackets inside another block.
- %OPTION% Variable c no longer exists outside the block.

[Reference](https://stackoverflow.com/a/6136865)
